  {
    "category": "merger",
    "datetime": 1780691400,
    "headline": "Boralex obtient l\u2019approbation d\u00e9finitive de la Cour pour r\u00e9aliser l\u2019arrangement avec Brookfield et La Caisse",
    "id": 8030651,
    "image": "https://res.cloudinary.com/whirlpooldata/image/upload/v1567047094/gnw_ngwqnq.png",
    "related": "",
    "source": "GlobalNewswire",
    "summary": "MONTR\u00c9AL,  05 juin 2026  (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Boralex inc. (\u00ab Boralex\u00a0\u00bb ou la\u00a0\u00ab\u00a0Soci\u00e9t\u00e9\u00a0\u00bb) (TSX\u00a0: BLX) a annonc\u00e9 aujourd\u2019hui que la Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 a obtenu une ordonnance d\u00e9finitive de la Cour sup\u00e9rieure du Qu\u00e9bec (chambre commerciale) approuvant le plan d\u2019arrangement r\u00e9gi par l\u2019article 192 de la Loi canadienne sur les soci\u00e9t\u00e9s par actions (l\u2019\u00ab\u00a0arrangement\u00a0\u00bb) annonc\u00e9 pr\u00e9c\u00e9demment et visant la Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 et BIF Thunder Holdings\u00a0Inc., une entit\u00e9 nouvellement constitu\u00e9e qui appartiendra conjointement \u00e0 Brookfield Infrastructure Fund V et/ou aux membres du m\u00eame groupe (collectivement, \u00ab\u00a0Brookfield\u00a0\u00bb) et \u00e0 la Caisse de d\u00e9p\u00f4t et placement du Qu\u00e9bec. Cette approbation d\u00e9finitive de la Cour fait suite \u00e0 l\u2019approbation des actionnaires obtenue \u00e0 l\u2019assembl\u00e9e annuelle et extraordinaire des actionnaires de la Soci\u00e9t\u00e9 tenue le jeudi 4\u00a0juin\u00a02026.",
    "url": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/06/05/3307619/0/fr/Boralex-obtient-l-approbation-d%C3%A9finitive-de-la-Cour-pour-r%C3%A9aliser-l-arrangement-avec-Brookfield-et-La-Caisse.html"
  },
  {
    "category": "merger",
    "datetime": 1780691400,
    "headline": "Boralex Obtains Final Court Approval of the Arrangement with Brookfield and La Caisse",
    "id": 8030650,
    "image": "https://res.cloudinary.com/whirlpooldata/image/upload/v1567047094/gnw_ngwqnq.png",
    "related": "",
    "source": "GlobalNewswire",
    "summary": "MONTR\u00c9AL, June  05, 2026  (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Boralex Inc. (\"Boralex\" or the \"Corporation\") (TSX: BLX) announced today that the Corporation has obtained a final order from the Superior Court of Qu\u00e9bec (Commercial Division) approving the previously-announced plan of arrangement under section 192 of the Canada Business Corporations Act (the \"Arrangement\") involving the Corporation and BIF Thunder Holdings Inc., a newly-formed entity to be jointly owned by Brookfield Infrastructure Fund V and/or its affiliates (collectively, \"Brookfield\") and Caisse de d\u00e9p\u00f4t et placement du Qu\u00e9bec. This final court approval follows the shareholder approval that was obtained at the annual and special meeting of the Corporation's shareholders held on Thursday, June 4, 2026.",
    "url": "https://www.globenewswire.com/news-release/2026/06/05/3307619/0/en/Boralex-Obtains-Final-Court-Approval-of-the-Arrangement-with-Brookfield-and-La-Caisse.html"
  },
